  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n\n    state \"Daemon Loop\" as loop {\n        state a <<choice>>\n        [*] --> action\n        action --> a\n\n        state \"Execute event\" as exec\n        note right of exec\n            status.events[i].executed = timestamp\n        end note\n\n        \n        a --> exec: node        \n        a --> exec: link\n        a --> [*]: end\n    }\n\n    state \"Created\" as c\n    note left of c\n        status.created = timestamp\n    end note\n\n    state \"Finished\" as done\n    note left of done\n        status.ended = timestamp\n    end note\n    \n    [*] --> c\n    c --> loop\n    loop --> done\n    done --> [*]\n",
