  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个后台守护进程的状态流转图。整体分成三个阶段：刚创建时的Created状态，中间有个循环处理事件的Daemon Loop，最后是Finished结束。起点和终点都用终止符表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created",
        "Daemon Loop",
        "Finished",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Created到Daemon Loop再到Finished是主线。Daemon Loop里面需要展开吗？看起来事件处理是核心逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created",
        "Daemon Loop",
        "Finished"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Daemon Loop要展开成复合状态。里面先有个action状态，然后到一个判断节点，根据类型走不同分支：node和link类型都进入Execute event执行，end类型就直接退出循环。Execute event执行完要记录时间戳。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Daemon Loop",
        "action",
        "choice",
        "Execute event",
        "node",
        "link",
        "end"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以Daemon Loop内部：action之后是条件判断，node和link都指向Execute event，end指向终止。Execute event右边加注释说明会更新status.events[i].executed。Created和Finished也加上时间戳注释，分别是created和ended字段，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Execute event",
        "Created",
        "Finished",
        "status.events[i].executed",
        "status.created",
        "status.ended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，注释都放在左侧比较整齐。Execute event的注释放右侧，因为那边空间更充裕。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Execute event",
        "Created",
        "Finished"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。Created在左边，Daemon Loop在中间复合展开，Finished在右边。Daemon Loop里的判断节点用菱形表示，三条出边分别标注了node、link和end。所有注释都按位置放好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created",
        "Daemon Loop",
        "Finished",
        "choice",
        "node",
        "link",
        "end"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，判断节点的标注我看下——end那条线应该是直接回到Daemon Loop外部的终止符，不是循环内部结束。还有，Execute event执行完之后应该回到哪里？现在看起来是隐式循环？",
      "elements_involved": [
